quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  48,16,Qul Lilmukhallafīna Mina Al-'A`rābi Satud`awna 'Ilá Qawmin 'Ūlī Ba'sin Shadīdin Tuqātilūnahum 'Aw Yuslimūna Fa'in Tuţī`ū Yu'utikumu Allāhu 'Ajrāan Ĥasanāan Wa 'In Tatawallaw Kamā Tawallaytum Min Qablu Yu`adhibkum `Adhābāan 'Alīmāan
  48,17,Laysa `Alá Al-'A`má Ĥarajun Wa Lā `Alá Al-'A`raji Ĥarajun Wa Lā `Alá Al-Marīđi Ĥarajun Wa Man Yuţi`i Allāha Wa Rasūlahu Yudkhilhu Jannātin Tajrī Min Taĥtihā Al-'Anhāru Wa Man Yatawalla Yu`adhibhu `Adhābāan 'Alīmāan
  48,18,Laqad Rađiya Allāhu `Ani Al-Mu'uminīna 'Idh Yubāyi`ūnaka Taĥta Ash-Shajarati Fa`alima Mā Fī Qulūbihim Fa'anzala As-Sakīnata `Alayhim Wa 'Athābahum Fatĥāan Qarībāan
  48,19,Wa Maghānima Kathīratan Ya'khudhūnahā Wa Kāna Allāhu `Azīzāan Ĥakīmāan
  48,20,Wa`adakumu Allāhu Maghānima Kathīratan Ta'khudhūnahā Fa`ajjala Lakum Hadhihi Wa Kaffa 'Aydiya An-Nāsi `Ankum Wa Litakūna 'Āyatan Lilmu'uminīna Wa Yahdiyakum Şirāţāan Mustaqīmāan
  48,21,Wa 'Ukhrá Lam Taqdirū `Alayhā Qad 'Aĥāţa Allāhu Bihā Wa Kāna Allāhu `Alá Kulli Shay'in Qadīrāan
  48,22,Wa Law Qātalakumu Al-Ladhīna Kafarū Lawallaw Al-'Adbāra Thumma Lā Yajidūna Walīyāan Wa Lā Naşīrāan
  48,23,Sunnata Allāhi Allatī Qad Khalat Min Qablu Wa Lan Tajida Lisunnati Allāhi Tabdīlāan